John L. CONLEY, Libelant-Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Respondent-Appellee. No. 124. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Feb. 1, 1932. Luden Y. Axtell, of New York City, for appellant. George Z. Medalie, U. S. Atty., of New York City (John C. Donovan, o£ New York City, of counsel), for the United States.

Before MANTON, SWAN, and AUGUSTUS N. HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed.
